            <description><![CDATA[
                
<h4><a name="UofMLocationandParking-DuderstadtCenter">Duderstadt Center</a></h4>

<p><span class="nobr"><a href="http://www.dc.umich.edu/" title="Visit page outside Confluence" rel="nofollow">http://www.dc.umich.edu/<sup><img class="rendericon" src="/confluence/images/icons/linkext7.gif" height="7" width="7" align="absmiddle" alt="" border="0"/></sup></a></span></p>

<p>Duderstadt Center<br/>
2281 Bonisteel Blvd.<br/>
Ann Arbor, Michigan 48109-2094<br/>
reception desk: 734-763-3266<br/>
fax: 734-936-3107</p>

<h4><a name="UofMLocationandParking-DirectionstotheDuderstadtCenter">Directions to the Duderstadt Center</a></h4>

<p>From the East, West and North, the Duderstadt Center is accessible from the Plymouth Road exit of US 23, the first exit on 23 south of M-14. Making a left onto Murfin Avenue from Plymouth Road will take you to the Visitor's Parking lot next to the Pierpoint Commons.</p>

<p>From the South, the Duderstadt Center is accessible from Bonisteel Boulevard, off of Fuller Road and Glazier Way.</p>

<h4><a name="UofMLocationandParking-Parking">Parking</a></h4>

<p>Please note that the parking area located directly north of Pierpont Commons and immediately to the northwest of the Duderstadt Center is now a building construction site.  This parking lot is reduced to 81 visitor parking spaces, 3 Staff (Blue) Handicap spaces, and 4 U-M Business spaces. Bonisteel Boulevard is now reduced to one lane of traffic in each direction in order to accommodate the addition of 70 parallel parking spaces. All these space are designated Blue permit parking M-F until 5:00 p.m. After 5:00 p.m., parking along Bonisteel Boulevard is available to the public.</p>

<p><img src="/confluence/download/attachments/5973/north_campus.gif" align="absmiddle" border="0" /></p>
            ]]></description>
