<p>A block of rooms have been reserved from July 17th through the 20th.  The room rate is $99.00 per night plus taxes. Check in time is 3:00PM and checkout is 11:00AM.  Parking is available on site for $10.00 per day if needed.  Anyone calling in should mention "Sakai Developers Gathering".  Reservations will be made on an individual basis.  An advance deposit for the first night's room and tax will be taken at the time the reservation is made.</p>

